            &mt LEFT_CONTROL A  &mt LALT S  &mt LEFT_COMMAND D  &mt LEFT_SHIFT F  &kp G          &kp H      &mt RSHFT J                     &mt LEFT_COMMAND K  &mt RALT L  &mt LEFT_CONTROL SEMICOLON
