        &mt LEFT_CONTROL LS(N5)   &mt LEFT_ALT LS(N7)   &mt LEFT_COMMAND RIGHT_BRACE  &mt LEFT_SHIFT LS(N0)  &kp RIGHT_BRACKET    &kp LEFT      &kp DOWN   &kp UP_ARROW  &kp RIGHT   &kp KP_MINUS
&trans  &kp LG(NON_US_BACKSLASH)  &kp NON_US_BACKSLASH  &kp CAPS                      &kp PG_DN              &kp F24              &kp RPAR      &kp HOME   &kp COMMA     &kp PERIOD  &kp SLASH     &mt LEFT_CONTROL DELETE
                                                        &kp BACKSPACE                 &trans                 &kp SPACE            &mo 3         &kp KP_N0  &trans
            >;
